data.description: This 3-bedroom ranch home features gleaming mahogany floors, open-concept living areas, and a convenient galley kitchen with custom cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, large pantry, and a coffee/wine bar. All bedrooms have new carpet, and the primary bedroom features a private en suite bathroom.  The home also has an enclosed attached garage, a 3000 sq ft driveway with brick edging, and a new detached 2-car garage. Located in a quiet neighborhood close to schools, parks, shopping, and dining. Just a short drive to the Virginia border and the Outer Banks.
